# Memory Optimization Results

This directory contains the output files from running the memory optimization simulations.

## Files

After running `run_all.py`, this directory will contain:

- `compression_results.json` - Compression strategy optimization results
- `eviction_results.json` - Eviction policy testing results
- `ann_results.json` - ANN index tuning results
- `sizing_results.json` - Cache sizing analysis results
- `prefetch_results.json` - Prefetching strategy results
- `unified_config.json` - Unified configuration from all optimizations
- `trace_analysis.json` - KV-cache access trace analysis

## Regenerating

To regenerate these files:

```bash
cd /path/to/polln
python simulations/optimization/memory/run_all.py
```

Or individually:

```bash
python simulations/optimization/memory/compression_optimization.py
python simulations/optimization/memory/eviction_policy.py
python simulations/optimization/memory/ann_index_tuning.py
python simulations/optimization/memory/cache_sizing.py
python simulations/optimization/memory/prefetching.py
```

## Note

These files are generated and should not be manually edited. Changes will be overwritten when optimizations are re-run.
